    "date": "2019-09-04T20:31:03Z",
    "text": "Stopping Grinch Bots Act of 2018\n\nThis bill prohibits the circumvention (e.g.,\u00a0via bot technology)\u00a0of a website's security measure or technological control for enforcing posted purchasing limits or for managing inventory. A person may not sell a product if the person knows that the product was acquired using such circumvention."
